<div class="inner mainContainer">

    <div>
        <h1>You Can Make It!!</h1>
        <h3>Thanks for checking out Ramseys Hell!</h3> <br><br> 

        <p>It's been well worth your time because here's
            what you can make in the allotted time and with your available ingredients!
        </p>
        <p>Good luck, enjoy your meal, and may the odds be ever in your favour!</p>
    </div>


    <div class="recipe-container">
        <div class="image-container">
